"Leads accepted by the partner are converted into *opportunities*. Clicking "
"an opportunity reveals the same information displayed in the **CRM** app, "
"but in a view designed for the user portal. From an opportunity's page, the "
"reseller may:"
msgstr ""
"Leads accepteret af partneren konverteres til *muligheder*. Klik på en "
"mulighed afslører de samme oplysninger, der vises i **CRM**-appen, men i en "
"visning designet til brugerportalen. Fra en muligheds side kan forhandleren:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/resellers.rst:174
msgid "Change the opportunity's stage."
msgstr "Ændre mulighedens fase."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/resellers.rst:175
msgid ""
"Edit the opportunity's information, including priority, planned revenue, and "
"pertinent dates."
msgstr ""
"Redigere mulighedens oplysninger, herunder prioritet, planlagt omsætning og "
"relevante datoer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/resellers.rst:176
msgid "Update the contact information for the opportunity."
msgstr "Opdatere kontaktoplysningerne for muligheden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/resellers.rst:177
msgid "Leave notes, messages, and more in the opportunity's chatter."
msgstr "Efterlade notater, beskeder og mere i mulighedens chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/resellers.rst:180
msgid ""
"The reseller's ability to change these settings depends on the access "
"granted to them by a database administrator. See the :doc:`access rights "
