"For at bruge UrbanPiper-integrationen i et live produktionsmiljø skal "
"følgende krav være opfyldt:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:43
msgid ""
"**UrbanPiper subscription:** A valid UrbanPiper subscription is mandatory."
msgstr ""
"**UrbanPiper-abonnement:** Et gyldigt UrbanPiper-abonnement er obligatorisk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:46
msgid ""
"For any concerns or queries regarding your UrbanPiper subscription, please "
"reach out to the account manager linked to your Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Ved spørgsmål eller bekymringer vedrørende dit UrbanPiper-abonnement bedes "
"du kontakte account manageren tilknyttet din Odoo-database."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:49
msgid "**Odoo requirements:**"
msgstr "**Odoo-krav:**"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:51
msgid ""
"**Odoo subscription:** An active Odoo Enterprise subscription is required. "
"Odoo Community does not support this integration."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo-abonnement:** Et aktivt Odoo Enterprise-abonnement er påkrævet. Odoo "
"Community understøtter ikke denne integration."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:53
msgid "**Odoo version:** Odoo Enterprise version 18.0 or above."
msgstr "**Odoo-version:** Odoo Enterprise version 18.0 eller nyere."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:54
msgid ""
"**Odoo platform:** All Odoo platforms are supported, including Odoo Online, "
"Odoo.sh, and On-Premise installations."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo-platform:** Alle Odoo-platforme understøttes, herunder Odoo Online, "
"Odoo.sh og On-Premise-installationer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:57
msgid ""
"**Delivery platform reseller account:** A registered reseller account is "
"required with each delivery platform to be integrated (e.g., Uber Eats, "
"DoorDash, Careem, Deliveroo, Zomato)."
msgstr ""
"**Leveringsplatform forhandlerkonto:** En registreret forhandlerkonto er "
"påkrævet hos hver leveringsplatform, der skal integreres (f.eks. Uber Eats, "
"DoorDash, Careem, Deliveroo, Zomato)."

